<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('../partials/head') %> <body class="bg-neo-white flex flex-col min-h-screen text-neo-black">
    
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <main class="flex-grow">
        
        <div class="bg-brand-slate text-white pb-20 pt-12 text-center border-b-4 border-black">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
                <span class="text-brand-indigo font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-4 inline-block font-inter">Who We Are</span>
                <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tighter font-display">
                    WE BUILD <br>
                    <span class="bg-white text-brand-slate px-4 border-4 border-brand-indigo shadow-neo inline-block transform -rotate-1 mt-2">FUTURE</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-medium border-l-4 border-brand-indigo p-6 bg-brand-slate/50 shadow-lg mt-8 font-inter italic">
                    // Not just an incubator. We are a factory of dreams, built with hard code and bold ideas.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
                <div class="bg-brand-indigo text-white border-4 border-black p-10 shadow-neo transform hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white text-brand-indigo border-4 border-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-4xl mb-6 shadow-sm">
                        🚀
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-4 uppercase font-display">The Vision</h2>
                    <p class="font-medium text-lg leading-relaxed border-l-4 border-white pl-4 font-inter text-indigo-100">
                        To create a structured ecosystem where developers turn coffee into scalable businesses. We believe in limitless potential.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-brand-slate text-white border-4 border-black p-10 shadow-neo transform hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white text-brand-slate border-4 border-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-4xl mb-6 shadow-sm">
                        🎯
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-4 uppercase font-display">The Mission</h2>
                    <p class="font-medium text-lg leading-relaxed border-l-4 border-white pl-4 font-inter text-slate-200">
                        Empowering 1000+ startups with solid tools. No corporate fluff, just straight-up value and robust backend logic.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 mb-24 max-w-4xl pt-10">
            <h2 class="text-5xl font-black text-center mb-16 underline decoration-brand-indigo decoration-8 underline-offset-8 font-display text-neo-black">OUR JOURNEY</h2>
            
            <div class="relative border-l-8 border-brand-slate ml-4 md:ml-1/2 md:pl-0 space-y-12">
                
                <div class="relative md:flex items-center justify-between group">
                    <div class="absolute -left-[14px] md:left-1/2 md:-ml-3 w-6 h-6 bg-brand-amber border-4 border-black rounded-full z-10"></div>
                    <div class="ml-10 md:ml-0 md:w-[45%] md:pr-8 md:text-right">
                        <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-6 shadow-neo-sm">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold bg-brand-amber text-black inline-block px-3 py-1 border-2 border-black mb-2 font-display">2024</h3>
                            <p class="font-medium font-inter text-slate-700">The idea was born in a garage. One server, zero funding, infinite ambition.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden md:block md:w-[45%]"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative md:flex items-center justify-between group">
                    <div class="absolute -left-[14px] md:left-1/2 md:-ml-3 w-6 h-6 bg-brand-indigo border-4 border-black rounded-full z-10"></div>
                    <div class="hidden md:block md:w-[45%]"></div>
                    <div class="ml-10 md:ml-0 md:w-[45%] md:pl-8">
                        <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-6 shadow-neo-sm">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold bg-brand-indigo text-white inline-block px-3 py-1 border-2 border-black mb-2 font-display">2025</h3>
                            <p class="font-medium font-inter text-slate-700">First 10 startups joined. We scaled the infrastructure and stabilized the core.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative md:flex items-center justify-between group">
                    <div class="absolute -left-[14px] md:left-1/2 md:-ml-3 w-6 h-6 bg-brand-slate border-4 border-black rounded-full z-10"></div>
                    <div class="ml-10 md:ml-0 md:w-[45%] md:pr-8 md:text-right">
                        <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-6 shadow-neo-sm">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold bg-brand-slate text-white inline-block px-3 py-1 border-2 border-black mb-2 font-display">2026</h3>
                            <p class="font-medium font-inter text-slate-700">Global expansion phase. Empowering developers worldwide.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden md:block md:w-[45%]"></div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-100 border-y-4 border-black py-16 mb-20">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl text-center">
                 <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-10 bg-white border-4 border-black inline-block px-8 py-3 shadow-neo-sm font-display uppercase tracking-widest">Key Metrics</h3>
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center gap-8">
                    <div class="flex-1 bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-neo hover:shadow-none hover:translate-x-1 hover:translate-y-1 transition-all">
                        <h4 class="text-6xl font-black mb-2 text-brand-indigo font-display">50+</h4>
                        <p class="text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-600 font-inter">Startups</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-neo hover:shadow-none hover:translate-x-1 hover:translate-y-1 transition-all">
                        <h4 class="text-6xl font-black mb-2 text-brand-indigo font-display">200+</h4>
                        <p class="text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-600 font-inter">Mentors</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-neo hover:shadow-none hover:translate-x-1 hover:translate-y-1 transition-all">
                        <h4 class="text-6xl font-black mb-2 text-brand-indigo font-display">∞</h4>
                        <p class="text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-600 font-inter">Coffees</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 mb-24 max-w-6xl">
            <h2 class="text-5xl font-black text-center mb-12 font-display text-neo-black">THE MANIFESTO</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <div class="border-4 border-black p-8 bg-white hover:bg-brand-slate hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 group shadow-neo">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-code text-4xl mb-6 text-brand-indigo group-hover:text-white"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 font-display">Code First</h3>
                    <p class="font-inter leading-relaxed font-medium">Talk is cheap. Show us the repo. We value builders and creators over talkers.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="border-4 border-black p-8 bg-white hover:bg-brand-slate hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 group shadow-neo">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-bolt text-4xl mb-6 text-brand-amber group-hover:text-white"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 font-display">Move Fast</h3>
                    <p class="font-inter leading-relaxed font-medium">Iterate quickly. Fail fast, learn faster. Just don't break production on Friday.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="border-4 border-black p-8 bg-white hover:bg-brand-slate hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 group shadow-neo">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-users text-4xl mb-6 text-brand-indigo group-hover:text-white"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 font-display">Community</h3>
                    <p class="font-inter leading-relaxed font-medium">A lone wolf dies, but the pack survives. We support and uplift each other.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 mb-12">
            <div class="bg-brand-slate text-white p-12 md:p-20 text-center border-4 border-black shadow-neo relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 font-display uppercase tracking-tighter">READY TO INNOVATE?</h2>
                    <p class="text-xl mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-slate-300 font-inter italic">Join the incubator that actually cares about your code quality, not just your pitch deck.</p>
                    <a href="<%= routes.signupRoute %>" class="inline-block bg-white text-brand-slate text-xl font-bold px-10 py-4 border-4 border-black shadow-neo hover:translate-y-1 hover:shadow-none transition-all font-display tracking-wide">
                        START BUILDING NOW
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-brand-indigo rounded-full opacity-20 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 blur-3xl"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-brand-indigo rounded-full opacity-20 translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/2 blur-3xl"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>